# Features Folder

This folder contains feature-specific design documentation.

Each feature should have its own subfolder with:
- README.md (use _templates/feature.md as a starting point)
- design-history.md (optional, for feature-specific history)
- context-sources.md (optional, for feature-specific sources)
- stakeholders.md (optional, if different from project-level)
- Dated iteration folders (e.g., 2025-01-21-initial-design/)

Example structure:
```
features/
├── context-sidebar/
│   ├── README.md
│   ├── design-history.md
│   └── 2025-01-21-initial-design/
│       ├── README.md
│       └── tasks.md
└── ai-assistant/
    ├── README.md
    └── ...
```
